snippet.title: Quake II RTX - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Quake II RTX, our ray-traced remaster of Quake II is now available to download and play! Check out the exclusive Official Launch Trailer for all the action that awaits you, all with GeForce RTX!

For more info on Quake II RTX, or to try out the free demo, visit: https://www.GeForce.com/QuakeIIRTX

Subscribe to GeForce! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCL-g3eGJi1omSDSz48AML-g?sub_confirmation=1

GeForce Twitter: https://twitter.com/NVIDIAGeForce
GeForce Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/NVIDIAGeForce/
GeForce Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/nvidiageforce/
